PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/1.1/Brick#>
PREFIX s223: <https://example.org/s223#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?property WHERE {
  {
    # Directly associated property
    ?zone a ?zoneClass .
    FILTER(?zoneClass = brick:Zone || ?zoneClass = s223:Zone) .
    ?zone brick:hasProperty ?property .
  }
  UNION
  {
    # Indirectly via a RoomDomainSpace (any length of connection)
    ?zone a ?zoneClass .
    FILTER(?zoneClass = brick:Zone || ?zoneClass = s223:Zone) .
    ?zone (brick:hasPart|brick:hasLocation|brick:hasSpace|s223:hasPart|s223:hasLocation|s223:hasSpace)* ?space .
    ?space a ?spaceClass .
    FILTER(?spaceClass = brick:RoomDomainSpace || ?spaceClass = s223:RoomDomainSpace) .
    ?space (brick:hasPart|brick:hasLocation|brick:hasSpace|s223:hasPart|s223:hasLocation|s223:hasSpace)* ?property .
  }
}
